##################
Vagrant VM Manager
##################

A thin wrapper around Vagrant to manage several virtual machines from one
place.

This script has been created to manage all project-related VMs from project's
root folder.


USAGE
=====

 1. Configure the settings.py file
 2. Use vm script :

    $ vm download
    $ vm start my_vm
    $ vm stop my_vm


COMMANDS
========

 - start vm_name
 - stop vm_name
 - download
 - configure vm_name
 - reconfigure vm_name
 - delete vm_name
 - ssh vm_name
 - restart vm_name
